display_long_description:
Proboscis! is a chaotic, action-packed VR experience inspired by Gorilla Tag — but with its own weird and wonderful twist. Climb, swing, and bounce your way through a growing world filled with unique maps, crazy game modes, and a bustling social hub where anything can happen.

Whether you're a competitive tag pro or just here to vibe, Proboscis! has something for everyone. Challenge your friends in a variety of modes, from classic tag to custom minigames, or explore the mall — a central hangout spot where you can shop, chill, and meet other players.

Key Features:

🦍 Physics-based movement – no buttons, just pure arm-powered fun

🏃‍♂️ Tons of game modes – from fast-paced tag to wild, experimental minigames

🛍️ A fully explorable mall packed with surprises

🎮 Frequent updates, seasonal events, and community-driven content

🧢 Cosmetic items and customization so you can express your inner Proboscis

Proboscis! is more than a game — it’s a growing world powered by the community. Join the chaos, make new friends, and see what’s around the next corner... or rooftop.

Are you ready to swing into the madness?
